name: MycoNetwork_[00]
description:
A swarm of mycelium networks fighting for food. A programming approach to growth patterns found underground, the internet of nature. This collection describes different patterns that can emerge while two colonies of funghi try to expand the mother cells in pursuit of growth, a fight for life.
Coded by a custom python script that generates numeric data used for mesh vertex displacement. by @arquiaz
